VHCS - Virtual Hosting Control System
==========================================================
Often it ain't what you do, it's the way you do it.

http://www.vhcs.net
http://www.molesoftware.com

VHCS software appliance provides complete hosting automation
for Linux platforms. VHCS Professional offers an easy-to-use graphical
interface for the administrators,resellers and domain owner
levels and complete functionality to manage the server and its components.

VHCS Pro was designed for professional Hosting Service
Providers (HSPs/ISPs) and IT-Professionals.

With VHCS Pro you can configure your server and aplications, create
user with domains with a few point-and-click operations that take
less than a minute. There is no limit to the number of resellers,
users and domains that can be created.


Enjoy the power of VHCS
moleSoftware / VHCS Team 
